high_descs: turn to the left at the green chair and make a left after passing the bed on the left, move forward across the room and make a left at the entry way to the bathroom,  move to the bathroom counter
pick up the black pen on the front middle edge of the bathroom counter
turn around to leave the bathroom, make a right into the room, move forward to the desk on the left and turn left to face the center of the desk
put the pen into the mug that is to the right of the lamp at the back of the desk
pick up the mug with the pen inside of it
turn to the left and move forward to the entry way of the bathroom on the left and turn to the left and move to the counter
put the mug with the pen on to the middle part of the counter
anns.task_desc: put a coffee mug with a pen inside of it on to the bathroom counter

high_descs: Turn to the left and the left again to go past the bed. Turn left in the next room and stand in front of the counter.
Pick up the pen that is to the front of the counter.
Take the pen and turn around. Turn right and then left to face the dining table.
Place the pen in the cup at the back of the table.
Pick up the cup from the back of the table.
Take the cup and turn to the left, then the left again to the counter.
Place the cup and pen in the center of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Move a cup and pen to the counter.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward, turn left, take a few steps, turn to your left again, and go to the white counter
Pick up the black pencil from the counter
Turn back and go to the black table with a yellow lamp across the room.
Place the pencil in the cup, which is on table
Pick up the cup with the pencil
Go back to the white counter from where you originally picked up the pencil
Place the cup with the pencil on the counter.
anns.task_desc: To put a pencil in a cup and place them on the counter.
